                <note rend="inline" type="source">560.M2/359: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        the Minister in Switzerland</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Wilson</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1933-07-07T17:00:00-04:00"
                            >July 7, 1933—5 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>34. Your 22, July 3, noon. Advise League that American Government’s withdrawal
                    applies also to supplementary agreement to convention and protocol signed July
                    11, 1928.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Phillips</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
